description: Indian investors saw a significant rise in wealth in FY 2024, with BSE market cap soaring. Despite global challenges, India's market showed resilience, attracting foreign investments and outperforming expectations.

description: Google Maps introduces new features, design updates, curated restaurant recommendations, hidden gems discovery, and AI-powered dish identification, enhancing the user experience for efficient navigation and travel planning.
title: Google Maps is getting a new look and three new features

description: Villupuram temple auctions lemons believed to cure infertility, bring prosperity. Villagers think lemons spiked in Lord Muruga's spear have magical powers. Traders, businessmen buy them. Couples visit during festival. A couple bought a lemon for Rs 50,500.
title: 9 lemons from TN temple sold for Rs 2.3 lakh

description: Harvinder Singh's journey from Punjab to a German refugee camp via Serbia highlights the exploitation of the Balkan route by an organized crime group. Deported after facing harsh conditions, Singh's case reveals the dangers of illegal immigration.
title: 'Donkey route' for a better life takes man to German refugee camp

description: An 84-year-old retired Army eye surgeon, Jadunath Mitra, found unconscious at their GC Block home in Salt Lake. His wife, Mandira Mitra, 73, dead with multiple stab wounds. Police treating as murder-attempted suicide.
title: 84-year-old doctor kills wife, tries to die by suicide in Kolkata

description: Japan's SLIM lander overcame lunar challenges, capturing new images post-frigid nights. JAXA aims to explore Moon's mantle. Private American lander Odysseus faced activation issues despite sunlight, disappointing its manufacturer.
title: Japan Moon probe survives second lunar night: Space agency

description: Emad Mostaque jokes about Satya Nadella's AI impact, sparking speculation. Microsoft excels in AI with top talent and key partnerships. Nadella praised as a leading CEO, while Mostaque explores decentralized AI.
title: 'In Satya we trust… ': AI startup founder ‘jokes’ about Microsoft CEO's influence

description: Kalyani Group plans to sue Sameer Hiremath and Pallavi Swadi for defaming Baba Kalyani over false allegations regarding family asset division, including Bharat Forge. Sameer and Pallavi face a defamation suit involving media disclosure, malicious intent, and an ownership dispute with their mother over Hikal.
title: Kalyani Group to sue Baba's nephew, niece

description: "We continue to follow these actions closely, including the arrest of Delhi CM Arvind Kejriwal. We are also aware of the Congress party's allegations that tax authorities have frozen some of their bank accounts in a manner that will make it challenging to effectively campaign in the upcoming elections," US State Department Spokesperson Matthew Miller said.
title: Now, US advocates 'fair' process on Congress bank accounts

description: Rachin Ravindra's fearless and aggressive batting in IPL, supported by CSK's strategic auction move and Michael Hussey's praise, highlights his impactful performances. Partnering with Ruturaj Gaikwad, he excels in powerplay overs on Indian grounds. Having set the world’s best T20 tournament ablaze with his lightning-quick knocks, Ravindra is proving to be one of the steals of the season.
title: Rachin Ravindra purchased for Rs 1.8 crore, proving to be a steal

description: A freight ship collision in Baltimore, US, was prevented from turning into a major disaster thanks to the alertness of the Indian crew on board the ship 'Dali'. President Joe Biden praised their quick response, emphasizing India's significant contribution to global shipping. The incident highlights the crucial role of Indian seafarers in ensuring maritime safety and efficiency.
title: How India became a talent pool for the global shipping industry
